Package: cfbscrapR
Title: A Scraping and Aggregating Interface to the CollegeFootballData API 
Version: 1.0.5
Authors@R: c(person('Saiem', 'Gilani', email = 'saiem.gilani@gmail.com', role = c('aut','cre')),
